	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=112394><span id= >jvickers</span></a><br><span id=notbold>3 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I've seen a lot of regen rates posted here for this item, ranging from 3hp to 12hp per tick, with the most common being 5hp/tick.<br><br>This item adds 5hp per tick and as far as I know is not level dependent (I'm level 60 and haven't tried it at other levels).<br><br>The reason some of you think that it adds 12hp/tick or is level dependent is that your *base* regen rate is level dependent.<br><br>A non iksar/troll, sitting, at level 60 regens 7 per tick.&nbsp;&nbsp;This item adds 5 to that for a *total* of 12.<br><br>I'm a 60 mage with 3aa in regen.  I get 20 per tick while sitting with this item and with my self buff up:  7 base (for being lvl 60), + 3aa + 5 for my tpp buff, +5 for the heart.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
